oji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3efb647566596f3527efce961ea384772dbd25","tid":427943,"uid":83321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:41:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出名運動員先係，點都唔屌得唔笑得<br />\n<br />\n唔出名或無成績既任屌唔嬲WFC<br />\n香港足球同欖球已經係例子，一輸波就話垃圾，瘋狂恥笑</blockquote><br />\n其實rugby女子隊唔差仲入埋世界盃但主流媒體一直唔覺有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e840aa35b6533700c8022907b418465047b7de30","tid":427943,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:44:40.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdde7b271dad9a80d8c6cb61aaf21e5116dbaed","tid":427943,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"「運動員」算唔算係香港種姓制度嘅最高階層?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/427943/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/427943/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我有冇睇錯？為咗反一個拳手竟然走去踩低「運動員」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你哋當初有咩資格笑梁振英講體育界對香港冇經濟貢獻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來你哋打從心底裏面都有同樣嘅想法<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/053407_760ba6b5963a3e3514671a9b5a45b92e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F053407_760ba6b5963a3e3514671a9b5a45b92e.jpg&h=96f27201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n引述返當時嘅媒體：<br />\n運動員付出了無數日子的汗水及努力，在國際賽事上取得佳績，為本港增光，這又如何計 ?況且就算某些人只向錢看，若說體育沒有經濟貢獻，也一樣說不過去。 <br />\n李慧詩稱，無論宗教和體育，在社會上都處於一個重要的地位，並影響社會的發展，更反問「關乎的何止是經濟貢獻」。"},{"pid":"c7a1d65b60238d3ee600fb33718c5eedb72c0bfd","tid":427943,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"有贊助商既運動員先係"},{"pid":"a9cf3b5582a0f25fcaa4a0be0d89a6904d82c418","tid":427943,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又一隻垃9圾波台狗</span></span>"},{"pid":"f0c9387c94b036f40af69f6521c8e0b57988acf0","tid":427943,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:54:41.000Z","msg":"運動員有政府出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 己經贏左我地小市民好多啦 梗係高等啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e14f32a99c01d99b97556cdac789ff764e2735","tid":427943,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"香港好多運動員要返多份正職糊口, 好心你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ac7715a6a09799af83168a6d59e408590702f6","tid":427943,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}